Cyberpunk style: A neon-lit industrial bakery interior at night, where glowing holographic data streams flow like ribbrant rivers between massive chrome mixing vats, conveyor belts carrying luminous cheesecakes, and towering ingredient silos. Each piece of equipment pulses with cyan and magenta circuitry patterns embedded in their surfaces. Translucent data threads connect raw ingredients in glass containers to finished cake slices, visualizing the journey of components through the production chain. Steam rises from machinery, catching the colored light. The scene has a gritty, rain-slicked floor reflecting the harsh artificial lights above. In the foreground, a single perfect slice of cheesecake sits on a plate, its layers visible and glowing faintly with embedded circuit-like patterns tracing back through gossamer digital threads to the various machines behind it, representing ingredient traceability through a complex system.
